job.title: IICB Project Associate Recruitment 2021 – Apply online for 09 Vacancies in Kolkata
job.body:
Total Vacancies: 09

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Senior Project Associate
  • Project Associate-II
  • Senior Project Associate
  • Technician  

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Graduates have been published by the Indian Institute of Chemical Biology for Senior Project Associate vacancies in Kolkata. If you are searching for a government job in Kolkata then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Senior Project Associate, from 22.05.2021, and till 04.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Kolkata and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for Senior Project Associate vacancies in Kolkata, your Degree, Master’s Degree  must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 22.05.2021.
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 04.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40 years old. 

IICB Senior Project Associate Pay Scale:

According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 42,000

How to apply for IICB Project Associate Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Senior Project Associate. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  • First, go to the official website of IICB and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by IICB
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
